            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the butternut squash is tender, remove the tray from the oven and add the <strong>roasted squash</strong> to the curry sauce</p><p>Stir until everything is well coated – this is your <strong>no butter chickpeas</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1670339858486-x200.jpg",
